verbose_text: In the current study, there was a statistically significant positive correlation between positive VEGF-A expression in portal structures in liver tissues with the degree of bile ductular proliferation (p < 0.05) in both studied groups, while there was a statistically significant positive correlation between positive VEGF-A in zone 1 and 2 hepatocytes with CK7 expression in liver tissues in the non BA group only (p < 0.05).
